	</p>
	
	<p>		
		rā<hi rend="grantha">jā</hi>tirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>-vaḷanāṭ 
		<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭut tirukkaḻumala<supplied reason="undefined">-nāṭṭut tiru</supplied>kkaḻumalat 
		<lb n="5" break="no"/>tu Uṭaiyār tiruttōṇipuram-uṭaiy 
		<lb n="6" break="no"/>ār kōyil <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> taṇṇir amu 
		<lb n="7" break="no"/>tu ceyta <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> paṭ 
		<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭarkaḷil <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
		<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṟṟattu <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> caruppēti 
		<lb n="10" break="no"/>-maṅkalat <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">dakṣi</hi>naimūrtti-pa 
		<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṭṭar I <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ṉṉiṉ vaṭṭil oṉṟiṉāl 
		<lb n="12"/>Oṉpatē <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> lē Araikkāl māṟi Eḻuttu 
		<lb n="13"/>veṭṭupa <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ṉ irupatt’ oṉpatiṉ kaḻañcē mukkāl 
	</p>
	         	
